### Variables
@apiVersion = /api/admin

###
### ============================================
### EMAIL VERIFICATION ENDPOINTS
### ============================================
###

### Verify Email - Success
# Replace {id} and {hash} with actual values from the email verification link
# Example: GET {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/auth/verify/1/abc123def456
GET {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/auth/verify/{id}/{hash}
Accept: text/html

### Verify Email - Invalid User ID
GET {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/auth/verify/99999/invalid-hash
Accept: text/html

### Verify Email - Invalid Hash
# Replace {id} with actual user ID
GET {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/auth/verify/{id}/invalid-hash
Accept: text/html

### Verify Email - Already Verified
# Replace {id} and {hash} with actual values from a user that is already verified
GET {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/auth/verify/{id}/{hash}
Accept: text/html

